Package com.khaledbakhit.api.rslib.exceptions

  • Exception Summary 
    Exception Description
    ClassificationsNotFoundException
    ClassificationsNotFoundException is thrown when classes file is not found.
    InputParseException
    InputParseException indicates parse failure of given input.
    InvalidInputException
    InvalidInputException indicates input is invalid.
    InvalidTypeIndexException
    InvalidTypeIndexException indicated provided index type is invalid.
    MetricsNotFoundException
    MetricNotFoundException is thrown when metric file is not found.
    SetupNotConfiguredException
    SetupNotConfiguredException occurs when a required variable within LaunchSetup Object that is null.
    UncleanDataSetException
    UncleanDataSetException indicates given dataset is of invalid/unsupported format.
    UnsupportedRuleSetFormatException
    UnsupportedRuleSetFormatException indicates parse error of input RuleSet.
